text: The OSIRIS-REx spacecraft has successfully stowed the sample collector head, which is full of surface material gathered from near-Earth asteroid Bennu, in the sample return capsule. This will prevent any more of the sample from leaking into space. https://t.co/VQU2qgGEIr
